Package com.gsma.mobileconnect.cache

Interface for a cache that is used by the Mobile Connect Discovery SDK IDiscovery.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDiscoveryCache
    Interface to the discovery response cache.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DiscoveryCacheHashMapImpl
    Implementation of IDiscoveryCache that uses a ConcurrentHashMap as a backing store.
    DiscoveryCacheKey
    Key for IDiscoveryCache entries.
    DiscoveryCacheValue
    Value that can be stored in an instance of the IDiscoveryCache.
